        What to Expect When Selling in Tarragindi
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Tarragindi is a quiet inner-south suburb bordered by Toohey Forest, offering family-focused streets and a buyer pool that has been benefiting from spillover from Holland Park and Greenslopes.
      </p>
